Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.35,0:00:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向往天空 亲近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.74,0:00:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翱翔于天空的神秘力量开始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.45,0:00:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.85,0:00:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有一个传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.15,0:00:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在天之边际云之彼方存在着一片黄金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.32,0:00:24.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个故事讲述了一个追寻梦想自由生存的天空盗贼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.11,0:00:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空盗团少年——酷的波澜起伏的爱和冒险的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.84,0:02:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在拉兹飞·安克鲁港镇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.74,0:02:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷和蕾遇到了欠下巨债的拉撒蒂和莉莉雅姐妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.98,0:02:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉撒蒂为了保护莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.63,0:02:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投身于在教堂废墟的地下深处的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.39,0:02:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个秘密的斗技场所举办的赌斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.53,0:02:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.30,0:02:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到煌珠被当作武器在使用的希丝卡他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到了十分激烈的冲击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.75,0:02:28.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此同时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.67,0:02:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正要款待酷和蕾的莉莉雅遭到了几个男人的袭击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.74,0:02:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去可不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.76,0:02:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未知的梦境{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.24,0:02:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.62,0:02:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,编织在一起{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.16,0:02:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并一直延续{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.70,0:02:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诱惑至深入{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.30,0:02:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使之闭目{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.07,0:03:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虚幻之路{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.37,0:03:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.56,0:03:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扫除全部{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.32,0:03:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛 眼睛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.44,0:03:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.28,0:03:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.28,0:03:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.34,0:03:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耍阴招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.78,0:03:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.45,0:03:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽美星夜{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.01,0:03:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牵引之线{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.69,0:03:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此倾心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.42,0:03:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在天之原{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.21,0:03:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追及之畏{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.10,0:03:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深藏在心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.52,0:03:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与我共颂念{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.60,0:03:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缔结契约{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.05,0:03:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气息相应{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.01,0:03:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠绕飞旋之风{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汝与我{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.61,0:03:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远相随{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.32,0:03:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤诚之心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.07,0:03:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缠绕飞扬之风{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,缔结契约{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.66,0:03:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.66,0:03:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是煌珠同契者啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.85,0:04:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.65,0:04:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第十唱 爱和欲望的赌斗场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 这真是意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.99,0:04:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不败的少虎拉撒蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.56,0:04:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受到对方的攻击后显得很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.77,0:04:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.52,0:04:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为标榜为不败的是个什么样的怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.37,0:04:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.67,0:04:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之所以没输过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我不能输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.99,0:04:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将斗气集中...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.06,0:04:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉像是要发动攻击了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.33,0:04:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一击将决定胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.61,0:04:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狂妄的小毛孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.76,0:04:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不败的名号就到此为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.93,0:04:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无论如何都不能输
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.24,0:04:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吼号穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.28,0:04:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.98,0:05:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是拉撒蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.87,0:05:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将那么巨大的对手轻易击倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有两下子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.66,0:05:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一击就将和煌珠同契的同契者打倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.22,0:05:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信的威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.11,0:05:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷 后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.30,0:05:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这样的怪物打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命有几条都不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.80,0:06:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.74,0:06:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.64,0:06:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.04,0:06:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.39,0:06:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.38,0:06:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.08,0:06:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天想掳走莉莉雅的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.17,0:06:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着同伙来袭击了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.64,0:06:55.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 总算被我们赶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.61,0:06:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.10,0:07:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.85,0:07:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.51,0:07:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.43,0:07:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把莉莉雅留在家里自己出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.11,0:07:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.90,0:07:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.87,0:07:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你们添麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.14,0:07:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙照顾帮了我们很大的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.14,0:07:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是我们道谢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.23,0:07:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救了莉莉雅两次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.90,0:07:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.08,0:07:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.55,0:07:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要遵守哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那女孩的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也要好好相处啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.61,0:08:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈真慢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望不要使事情复杂化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.06,0:08:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情有了完善的解决方案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.54,0:08:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.35,0:08:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将在赌斗场展开大规模的彻底的煌珠保护作战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.21,0:08:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.13,0:08:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉兹飞·安克鲁分部答应派出援军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.32,0:08:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.99,0:08:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要再次潜入赌斗场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.30,0:08:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等待援军到来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.24,0:08:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要穿这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好吗 龙威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.30,0:08:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到很配你嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.71,0:08:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾他们怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.97,0:08:53.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不联系他们没关系吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.48,0:08:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以用煌珠雷达探测到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.38,0:08:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.66,0:09:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等作战结束后再汇合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那个 问题是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.32,0:09:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.82,0:09:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷他们有没有在努力赚钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.25,0:09:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果昨天我们两个都被解雇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.06,0:09:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被希丝卡知道还没赚到一分钱的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.92,0:09:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被杀掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.86,0:09:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道就没有能快速赚到钱的方法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.35,0:09:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个的话我倒有个好办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.52,0:09:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是来告诉你好消息的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.01,0:09:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.59,0:09:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要钱的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.40,0:09:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去山岗上的教堂废墟看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.95,0:09:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会相信你的鬼话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.74,0:09:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一到晚上那里的地下就有格斗比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.39,0:09:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取胜的话可以得到很多奖金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.47,0:10:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都有这么厉害的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.48,0:10:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许能赚很多钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.39,0:10:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想干的话是不会逼你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.44,0:10:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看我这样 我可是很好心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.29,0:10:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉你进入会场的暗号吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.62,0:10:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟在教堂废墟的入口处的黑衣人这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.70,0:10:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要呼唤女神 机会就会降生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.30,0:10:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,望着脚下之地 有着主的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.23,0:10:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叽哩咕噜的真啰嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.98,0:10:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.05,0:10:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.66,0:10:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是昨晚的奖金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.50,0:10:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这笔钱我马上交给那伙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.92,0:11:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚好像陷入了苦战 没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.62,0:11:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.84,0:11:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要太勉强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.90,0:11:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚还是不要出场的好……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.74,0:11:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是想出场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.23,0:11:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玛鲁先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.43,0:11:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.59,0:11:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是在今晚的比赛中获胜的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.60,0:11:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那奖金应该就能彻底还清父母亲欠下的债
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.39,0:11:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样一来莉莉雅就能自由了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.75,0:11:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.24,0:11:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以不用再担惊受怕会被谁带走了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.75,0:11:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我想是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.02,0:11:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.23,0:12:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚来看我的比赛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.63,0:12:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚的事也许会再发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.34,0:12:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不放心让你一个人在家里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.90,0:12:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.51,0:12:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今晚一定会赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后让你获得自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.91,0:12:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和你分享那个瞬间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.60,0:12:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.92,0:12:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失手了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.30,0:12:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.04,0:12:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉撒蒂那家伙把欠款全部还清的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.65,0:12:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不能再束缚莉莉雅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.89,0:12:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以命令你在那之前绑架莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没用的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.88,0:12:51.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到来了个搅和的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.84,0:12:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蹩脚的借口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个奇怪的煌珠同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.10,0:13:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.96,0:13:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想绝对很值钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一看脸就明白……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.76,0:13:05.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎样的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.30,0:13:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同契者只是个小毛孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.20,0:13:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煌珠倒是很厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.34,0:13:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会变成一把巨大的剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.48,0:13:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能自由自在地操控风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.50,0:13:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.67,0:13:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人要雇我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.90,0:13:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不容易啊 赚钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.84,0:13:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.27,0:13:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那人说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.19,0:13:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山岗上的教堂废墟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.32,0:13:45.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种人知道的肯定不是什么好地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.14,0:13:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先不说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.27,0:13:49.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能让蕾去冒险呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.97,0:13:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是没钱的话不就去不了煌珠乐园了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.60,0:13:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.01,0:13:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为那样 为了去那里而让蕾去战斗什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.61,0:14:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说好要带蕾去煌珠乐园的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.43,0:14:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.65,0:14:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不想要酷来保护我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.96,0:14:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不想要酷做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.95,0:14:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.25,0:14:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.00,0:14:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想和酷在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.35,0:14:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和蕾在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.50,0:14:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.11,0:14:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.34,0:14:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.41,0:14:52.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两个就去捣乱一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.23,0:15:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要呼唤女神 机会就会降生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,望着脚下...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.24,0:15:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,望着脚下...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.78,0:15:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是什么来着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.87,0:15:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,望着脚下之地 有着主的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.74,0:15:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那里干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.59,0:16:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弄成这副装束在干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是有任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.94,0:16:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任务？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.07,0:16:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里在举办赌钱的格斗赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.24,0:16:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多煌珠同契者参加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 酷也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.98,0:16:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.42,0:16:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷 你这个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.64,0:16:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我们的任务是保护煌珠 还...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.23,0:16:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这和我没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.56,0:16:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说要我们赚钱的不是你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.47,0:16:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不能因此而...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和蕾约好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.18,0:16:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去煌珠乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾没意见吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.90,0:16:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种地方打斗什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就当作什么都没看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.14,0:16:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样才对嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.74,0:16:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系吗 前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.54,0:17:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷若仅仅只是想要赚钱的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.87,0:17:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾是不可能和他一起战斗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.66,0:17:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.91,0:17:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.16,0:17:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是对于他们来说还是对于我们来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.47,0:17:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都会是找到什么问题的机会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.15,0:17:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.15,0:17:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了能确确实实地将这里所有的煌珠保护起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.53,0:17:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须等待援军的到来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.56,0:17:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.68,0:17:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不要让人知道是守护翼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.22,0:17:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当自己是客人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.21,0:17:30.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.83,0:17:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里举行的比赛是赌钱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.04,0:17:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.91,0:17:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.00,0:17:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那些没胜算的家伙身上下注
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.28,0:17:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是赢了的话不是能赚很多钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.38,0:17:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.33,0:17:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,押在酷身上怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.55,0:17:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算蕾有多么厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.73,0:17:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同契者是酷的话要想赢就还...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.86,0:17:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.65,0:17:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是觉得很可行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.96,0:18:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.32,0:18:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷若是状态不错的话好像能超常发挥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.65,0:18:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能那么顺利吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.70,0:18:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真是惊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.19,0:18:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷德·望·朱鲁爱特初次登台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.29,0:18:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一击就将对手巴狄·多拉打得丧失战斗力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.97,0:18:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们两人联手的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.70,0:18:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子就能搞定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.68,0:18:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.61,0:18:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是梅札兰斯一族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.04,0:18:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得档次不同吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.28,0:18:37.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 蕾和酷的同步率高得惊人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.75,0:18:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.76,0:18:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.98,0:18:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能实现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.81,0:18:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是在做梦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南风之弦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.52,0:19:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东风之钚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.42,0:19:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不累吗 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.60,0:19:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.21,0:19:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一鼓作气赢到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.45,0:19:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.52,0:19:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.91,0:19:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了你 这点伤算不了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.08,0:19:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是玛鲁先生不是说过吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.23,0:19:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太勉强比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.64,0:19:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤成这样了还要去战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.96,0:19:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再让姐姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.50,0:19:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说了不用担心的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.01,0:19:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今晚一定会赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了让你重获自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.75,0:19:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.77,0:20:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.94,0:20:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去斗技场等我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.77,0:20:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让各位久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.69,0:20:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决战即将开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.14,0:20:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先介绍的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.92,0:20:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是第一次露面却一口气赢到现在的新人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.98,0:20:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷德·望·朱鲁爱特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.66,0:20:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.61,0:20:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.70,0:20:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的全部财产都押在你身上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.21,0:20:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要打她个落花流水 知道了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.63,0:20:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.21,0:20:52.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.22,0:20:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管对手是怎样的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.85,0:20:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.18,0:20:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.13,0:20:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的对手是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.38,0:20:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赌斗场的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.03,0:21:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不败的少虎
